title: Hokies return to Ann Arbor for NCAA Regionals - VT hokiesports.com
content: Hokies return to Ann Arbor for NCAA Regionals  VT hokiesports.com
description: The Virginia Tech women's golf team is set to compete in its fourth consecutive NCAA regional, Monday-Wednesday, in Ann Arbor, Michigan. The three-day event is being hosted by Michigan at the par 71, 6,265-yard U-M Golf Course.
